description: This is it boys and girls! It’s the series where everything happens! SpyBoy comes face to face with his greatest challenges ever—his senior prom, his graduation from high school ... and the revelation as to the truth about his mother! All this while going up against his greatest opponent ever—Spyguy!
name: Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, SPYGUY.

description: Witness the cosmic conclusion of Captain America’s most epic challenge yet! Marvel's man out of time has met his match in the omnipotent Michael Korvac, a freak of science from the future. Yesterday and tomorrow are on a collision course…but will any of it matter in the shadow of Galactus the world devourer.
name: The Star Lord

description:
Romulus has lured Wolverine to a Russian prison with a very dangerous inmate: Omega Red! Old scores are settled as Wolvie clashes with one of his most hated enemies!

By Daneil Way and Scot Eaton.

Also: Deadpool has fallen for the Black Widow, the leader of the new Thunderbolts – but that won’t stop him kicking all their butts! Will Norman Osborn get his revenge on the Merc with the Mouth?!

By Andy Diggle and Bong Dazo.

Includes material reprinted from Wolverine: Origins #38-39 and Thunderbolts #131.
